SUMMARY:Children's Fairyland — Oakland
DESCRIPTION:A gentle\, storybook-themed park made for little kids — their
  first puppet show\, first tiny carousel ride\, and walk-through fairy-ta
 le sets they can toddle through. No big crowds or scary rides.\nDrive: ~3
 0 min from Fremont\nWebsite: https://fairyland.org
LOCATION:Children's Fairyland\, Oakland CA
URL:https://fairyland.org
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
