SUMMARY:Little Farm + Merry-Go-Round\, Tilden Park — Berkeley
DESCRIPTION:Get nose-to-nose with cows\, goats\, sheep\, and chickens at 
 the free Little Farm (public feeding ended in 2026\, so it's look-and-wat
 ch now)\, then a first spin on the vintage carousel and the Redwood Valle
 y steam train nearby.\nDrive: ~40 min from Fremont\nWebsite: https://www.
 ebparks.org/parks/tilden-nature-area
LOCATION:Little Farm Tilden Regional Park Berkeley CA
URL:https://www.ebparks.org/parks/tilden-nature-area
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
