SUMMARY:Farm Cottage Stay · Mar Vista\, Gualala — Gualala (Mendocino Coas
 t)
DESCRIPTION:Rent a restored 1930s cottage (fireplace\, full kitchen\, pri
 vate bath) on a 9-acre organic farm on the 'secret coast.' Your little gu
 y collects warm eggs at the daily Chicken Chat\, feeds the goats at Goat 
 Gab\, picks veggies straight from the garden\, and toddles down to a priv
 ate beach. Pure\, screen-free magic.\nDrive: ~3 hrs from Fremont\nWebsite
 : https://marvistafarmandcottages.com/
LOCATION:Mar Vista Farm and Cottages\, 35101 CA-1\, Gualala CA
URL:https://marvistafarmandcottages.com/
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
