SUMMARY:Gilroy Gardens Family Theme Park — Gilroy
DESCRIPTION:A garden theme park built for the littlest riders: their firs
 t tiny rides with low height limits\, a first paddle boat\, splash areas\
 , and acres of grass. Gentle\, green\, and genuinely toddler-scaled.\nDri
 ve: ~45 min from Fremont\nWebsite: https://www.gilroygardens.org
LOCATION:Gilroy Gardens Family Theme Park Gilroy CA
URL:https://www.gilroygardens.org
