SUMMARY:Sonoma TrainTown Railroad — Sonoma
DESCRIPTION:A 20-minute miniature train ride through tunnels and over lit
 tle bridges — a thrilling first train for a 19-month-old — plus a petting
  zoo\, carousel\, and a kid-sized Ferris wheel. Built for the under-5 cro
 wd.\nDrive: ~1 hr 30 min from Fremont\nWebsite: https://traintown.com
LOCATION:TrainTown Sonoma CA
URL:https://traintown.com
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
