SUMMARY:Airstream in the Redwoods · AutoCamp Russian River — Guerneville
DESCRIPTION:Sleep in a design-forward vintage Airstream (private bath\, r
 eal beds\, AC) under a grove of giant redwoods. Borrow the free bikes\, t
 oast s'mores at your own fire pit\, do morning kids' crafts at the clubho
 use\, and drift along the gentle Russian River beach just minutes away.\n
 Drive: ~2 hrs from Fremont\nWebsite: https://autocamp.com/location/sonoma
 /
LOCATION:AutoCamp Russian River\, 14120 Old Cazadero Rd\, Guerneville CA
URL:https://autocamp.com/location/sonoma/
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
