SUMMARY:CuriOdyssey — San Mateo
DESCRIPTION:A bayside science playground where toddlers push\, pour\, and
  poke at interactive exhibits and meet rescued native animals up close. S
 mall\, manageable\, and endlessly touchable — a great first museum of dis
 covery.\nDrive: ~35 min from Fremont\nWebsite: https://curiodyssey.org
LOCATION:CuriOdyssey San Mateo CA
URL:https://curiodyssey.org
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
